questions.text:
Quyidagi for sikli nechta raqamni konsolga chiqaradi?
```js
let count = 0;
for (let i = 2; i < 10; i += 2) {
  console.log(i);
  count++;
}
console.log("count:", count);
```

forEach bilan massivdagi juft sonlarni nechta ekanligini sanaydigan kod natijasi?
```js
const a = [3,6,1,8,4];
let c = 0;
a.forEach(n => { if (n % 2 === 0) c++; });
console.log(c);
```

Quyidagi kod nima chiqaradi?
```js
const arr = [10, 20, 30];
for (let i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) {
  if (i === 1) continue;
  console.log(arr[i]);
}
```

Nested for: nechta yulduzcha chiqadi?
```js
let s = "";
for (let i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
  for (let j = 0; j < 2; j++) {
    s += "*";
  }
}
console.log(s.length);
```

Index bilan forEach ishlatish: quyidagi natija nima?
```js
const a = ['a','b','c'];
a.forEach((v,i)=>{ if(i===1) console.log(v); });
```

Massiv ichidagi massiv: nechta satr hosil bo‘ladi?
```js
const grid = [[1,2],[3,4],[5,6]];
let rows = 0;
for (let i = 0; i < grid.length; i++) {
  rows++;
}
console.log(rows);
```

Ichki massiv elementlarini yig‘ish: natija?
```js
const grid = [[1,2],[3],[4,5]];
let sum = 0;
for (let i = 0; i < grid.length; i++) {
  for (let j = 0; j < grid[i].length; j++) {
    sum += grid[i][j];
  }
}
console.log(sum);
```

break ishlatilganda natija?
```js
const xs=[5,7,9,11];
for (let i=0;i<xs.length;i++){
  if(xs[i]===9) break;
}
console.log("done");
```

continue bilan natija?
```js
for (let i=0;i<4;i++){
  if(i===2) continue;
  console.log(i);
}
```

forEach callback ichida return nima qiladi?
```js
[1,2,3].forEach(n=>{
  if(n===2) return;
  console.log(n);
});
```

Nested forEach va for — natija?
```js
const g=[[1,2],[3,4]];
let out=[];
g.forEach(row=>{
  for(let i=0;i<row.length;i++){
    out.push(row[i]*2);
  }
});
console.log(out.join(','));
```

Ichma-ich massivdagi juft sonlar yig‘indisi?
```js
const m=[[2,5],[4],[1,3,6]];
let s=0;
for (let r of m) {
  for (let x of r) if (x%2===0) s+=x;
}
console.log(s);
```

forEach sinxronmi? Natija qachon chiqadi?
```js
const a=[1,2,3];
a.forEach(n=>console.log(n));
console.log('end');
```

for bilan massivga push qilish: yakuniy uzunlik?
```js
const r=[];
for(let i=1;i<=5;i++){ r.push(i*i); }
console.log(r.length);
```

Scope: for ichidagi let o‘zgaruvchi tashqarida mavjudmi?
```js
for(let k=0;k<1;k++){}
console.log(typeof k);
```

forEach ichida massivni o‘zgartirish: natija?
```js
const a=[1,2,3];
a.forEach((v,i)=>{ a[i]=v*3; });
console.log(a.join('-'));
```

Nested indekslar: natija?
```js
const m=[[0,1],[2,3,4]];
let s='';
for(let i=0;i<m.length;i++){
  for(let j=0;j<m[i].length;j++){
    if((i+j)%2===0) s+=m[i][j];
  }
}
console.log(s);
```

forEach indeks bilan filtr: natija?
```js
const a=['x','y','z','w'];
let r=[];
a.forEach((v,i)=>{ if(i%2===0) r.push(v); });
console.log(r.join(','));
```

for va continue bilan ichki sikl: nechta log?
```js
let c=0;
for(let i=0;i<3;i++){
  for(let j=0;j<3;j++){
    if(j===1) continue;
    c++;
  }
}
console.log(c);
```

for...of bilan stringdagi harflar sanog‘i?
```js
let s='abaac';
let cnt=0;
for(const ch of s){ if(ch==='a') cnt++; }
console.log(cnt);
```
